title: James Diekmann Honorary Award Fund
description: To provide support for the James Diekmann Honorary Award to be awarded to alumni or industry leader each year at the CEM graduation dinner in honor of Professor Emeritus, James Diekmann.
marketingContent: Project raises funds for the James Diekmann Honory Award to be awarded to alumni or industry leader each year at the CEM graduation dinner in honor of Professor Emeritus, James Diekmann.
